I '''Satyajit Ray''' ({{lang|bn|Shôtôjit Rae}}, {{Audio|SatyajitRay2.ogg|listen}}; 2 Mayo 1921&nbsp;– 23 Abril 1992) metung yang talagawang pelikulang Indian a tuturing dang metung kareng pekamapyang [[auteur]] (''greatest auteurs'') ning yatu ning pelikula. Mibait ya i Ray king lakanbalen o syudad ning [[Calcutta]] king pamilyang  [[Bengali (lahi)|Bengali]]ng sikat king yatu ning arte ampong literatura. Inumpisan na ing kayang karera antimong ''commercial artist'' i Ray, a milub king pamangawang timawang pelikula (''independent film'') i Ray kaybat dang mikit ning talagawang pelikulang Pranses a i  [[Jean Renoir]], at ayalben ne ing pelikula nang [[Vittorio De Sica]]ng [[Italian neorealism|Italian neorealist]] anyang 1948 a ''[[Bicycle Thieves]]'' anyang binisita ya king London.

Migdirek yang 36 a pelikula i Ray, kayabe la reng ''feature film'', documentary ampong [[short subject|short]]. Metung ya muring talasulat pisyon He was also a (''fiction writer''), talalimbag (''publisher''), talagulis (''illustrator''), ''calligrapher'', ''graphic designer'' ampong kritikung pangpelikula. Sinulat yang mapilan a makuyad a salita He authored several (''short stories'') ampong nobela, a keraklan makatutuk kareng anak ampng kayanakan. I [[Feluda]], ing detektib, ampo ing the sleuth, ampo i [[Professor Shonku]], ing siyentista, sikat lang tauan king piksyon a lelangan na.  

Sinambut yang labing metung a galal a internasyunal ing mumuna nang pelikulang Ray, ing ''[[Pather Panchali]]'' (1955), kayabe ya ing ''Best Human Documentary'' king [Cannes Film Festival]]. Ining pelikula, ing ''[[Aparajito]]'' (1956) ampo ing ''[[The World of Apu|Apur Sansar]]'' (1959) bibilugan de ing ''[[The Apu Trilogy]]''. I Ray ing ginawa king [[screenplay|scripting]], casting, [[Film score|scoring]], ampong editing, at ya ing migdisenyu king sarili nang ''credit title'' ampong publisidad. Dakal ya tinggap a manimunang galal i Ray king kayang karera, kayabe la reng 32 Indian [[National Film Awards]], pilang galal kareng internasyunal a ''film festival'' ampong seremonyang pamamye galal, ampong [[Academy Award]] anyang 1992. Peparangalan ne nng [[Kapamahalan ning India]] kapamilatan ning [[Bharat Ratna]] anyang 1992.

